"We need to borrow a space shuttle," said Brix back into the 
comlink, "There is a large deposit of materials on the moon when a 
star ship crashed their a few months ago. Only the engines went out, 
so the rest of it is okay. We want to use the shuttle to retrieve 
parts to re-build the Ark. May we meet you in the shuttle bay?"
